*Desilo* se da je posle kiše sve bilo oblačno. (It happened that after the rain, everything was cloudy.)

*Desilo* se da je njegova mašta daleko od njegove stvarnosti. (It happened that his imagination was far from his reality.)

*Desila* se nesreća u gradu. (An accident happened in the city.)

*Desilo* se da je putovao za drugim gradom. (It happened that he traveled to another city.)

*Deseo* se da će mu se želja ostvariti. (He wished that his wish would come true.)